channel.title: CiTR -- Passing Binary (2007)
channel.description: Passing Binary inspired by techno-logy and its evolvement are planning change - steps have been calculated, the plan is initiated. We will control the future as we make techno-logy our tool to spread the message. Our aim is to bring this music to the fore as the other forms die out.
